title: "The Friction We Can't Afford to Lose"
date: "2026-04-23"
description: "AI should remove chores, not load-bearing friction. In learning, the dangerous shortcut is not automation itself but skipping the effort that builds judgment."
tags: ["ai", "education", "learning", "cognition"]
